videos.description: Michigan State puts on the exclamation point in their win over Ohio State with Alvin Ellis III tossing the ball off the backboard for Matt Van Dyk to fly in for the massive two-handed put back.
videos.headline: Off-the-backboard alley-oops are always a good time

videos.headline: Valentine: We settled down in the second half
